# Libs Directory

Shared libraries and utilities that can be used across all apps.

Organize by feature or type:
```
src/libs/
├── utils/          # General utilities
├── hooks/          # React hooks
├── components/     # Shared React components
├── types/          # TypeScript types
└── api/            # API clients
```

Import from apps using the @/ alias:
```typescript
import { formatCount } from '@/libs/utils/format';
import { useDebounce } from '@/libs/hooks/useDebounce';
```
